CodeFellows Jeopardy

CodeFellows Jeopardy is a fun way for 100 & 200 level students to prepare for their quizzes and final exams. This quiz game covers concepts learned during the 102 and 201 classes.

  • Five category, basic Jeopardy style trivia game.
  • Great use of CSS and JavaScript to display questions on a modal window and black out the cards that have been selected.
  • Intuitive and easy to use.
